gov.nasa.gsfc.nisgs.dsm.agent.rdr
Class NPOESSFilename

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.gsfc.nisgs.dsm.agent.rdr.NPOESSFilename

public class NPOESSFilename
extends java.lang.Object

Creates legal NPOESS (JPSS) filenames. The format is to mission specification. This is taken from RT-STPS, modified slightly to provide just the functionality needed by RDRMover.
